Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Clover] All right, gather round.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mission today is to\Nsecure the launch site
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Amity Communications Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The designated area is\Nan abandoned Dust mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Since its closure, the\NGrimm have moved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The good news is all that untouched Dust
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is still down there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Science team says they'll need it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,for the first phase of their launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Pietro] Apologies for the mess
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and for holding onto\Nyour weapons for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The upgrades you requested were, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,well, they were more than\NI anticipated (laughs).
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Clover] Atlas military huntsmen\Nare already hard at work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,clearing out the surrounding tundra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But recon has identified a powerful Geist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that's managed to evade\Ndestruction and take several lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,After we increased our numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the Geist were smart enough to\Nretreat into the mine itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning it's old, and extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our target.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Pietro] Your new weapons and armor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,should be as requested,\Nbut I also took the liberty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,of reviewing your combat footage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,from the Vytal Festival Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some additional\Nenhancements I'd like to suggest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but for now, these\Nshould serve you well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- The mine was a labyrinth back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's all sorts of tunnels and chambers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the Geist can move between,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so if we're gonna kill this thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have to split up and corner it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,General Ironwood says you've\Nseen your fair share of combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust that man with\Nmy life, so tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be trusting you all, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Clover] Let's make it happen, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Weiss] Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,(Yang laughs)\N- Hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh! (laughs)
