Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is my favorite part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- (laughs) Perhaps you kids
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,won't get yourselves killed after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmph!\N(Jaune groans)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- She meant that as a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,(device chirps)\N- This is Alpha squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,LZ's clear, proceeding on foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've all got fancy new scrolls,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:04:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so don't forget to use 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your eyes and ears open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I want an update if you\Nencounter the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Alpha out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Uh, sorry, just not\Nused to the new hair yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is it bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Yang] No, no, it's good, great even!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Man, I did not sign\Nup to be a babysitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, well, the rest of\Nus babysit you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, it's freezing out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Without heating or projected Aura,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the cold of Solitas can kill\Nyou in a matter of hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- I suddenly don't feel as bad\Nabout leaving Oscar behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- (sighs) Can we talk about that again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're really not gonna tell\NIronwood what happened to Oz?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What we learned about Jinn, about Salem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- We are, we will,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but you saw how things looked\Nwhen we flew into Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- The General's heart seems\Nto be in the right place,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't mean\Nwe should trust him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- We need to play along for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,before we make any major decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay, how did Oscar feel about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ruby] Er, probably shouldn't\Nkeep running around
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,with an ancient relic\Non a keychain, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- But --\N- I know you'll
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,keep it safe in Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ruby, hiding things from Ironwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't that feel like\Nwhat Ozpin did to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Gotta say, I'm still\Nnot really used to working
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,with other huntsmen in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- But you were on a team\Nbefore, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- (sighs) Long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I just found working alone\Ntends to be for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, I think that's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!\N(Clover grunts)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Qrow] Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Alpha here, gimme an update.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- The connecting ice tunnels seem clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be approaching the\Nactual mine any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like we're an\Nactual huntsmen team!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I, um, like what you did\Nwith your outfit, Ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- We should probably stay\Nfocused on the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- I like your outfit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmph.\N- [Harriet] Bravo checking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit a bit of a snag.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been a cave-in\Nin the main entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sure if it's recent
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or was caused by the original accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, we'll have to\Ndo a little problem solving.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Clover] Understood, let us\Nknow if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- I just realized where we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This mine was closed after an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- I remember this disaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,or rather, I remember how\Nfurious it made my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:07:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(sighs) I wish I could\Ntake back the years of pain
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,my family has caused the Faunus,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of my complacency in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- This society is set up for\NFaunus to be at the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and humans are willing participants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They benefit from doing\Nnothing to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are still those\Nwho actively abuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I didn't come\Nover here looking to solve
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,systemic societal issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Harriet found a gap in the\Nrubble we think one of you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,could fit through, ideally\Nsomeone with a knack
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.39,0:08:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,for seeing in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Marrow] All right,\NBlake, take a look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any Dust in the immediate area?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mine carts... debris...\Nno Dust, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Marrow] Great, then it should be safe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to blast our way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay, heading back.\N(creature whooshing)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:09:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Damn it, Blake, stand back. (shouts)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't let it get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.70,0:09:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:10:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ha!\N(creature shrieking)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is Bravo, we found the target,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but it fled deeper into the\Nmine. Engaging Centinels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's pick up the pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Whoa, uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- A very... head-first approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, well, that's\Njust kind of our style.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- One left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, your Semblance makes\Nyou super fast, just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Very cool, though based\Non your reaction time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say I'm a little faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Clover] This is Alpha,\Nwe've engaged the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All squads head towards our position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- (Clover grunts)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- Darn it, target escaped,\Nlast seen headed east.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the call-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That could have been bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- (sighs) I wouldn't thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My Semblance brings misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I can't keep it under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Clover] That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hey, don't beat\Nyourself up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My Semblance is good fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Charlie, Bravo, you should\Nbe able to cut off the target
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,at the heart of the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Qrow and I won't be far behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Guys!\N- [Vine] Everyone use caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- This room is highly\Nactive with Dust energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Triggering it could ruin the launch site.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Marrow] And vaporize us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that always second with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- I thought the target was\Nsupposed to be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- It added Dust to its body?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- Elm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- (grunts) Vine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- (grunts) Marrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ha!\N(weapon whooshing)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,(grunts) Harriet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- (laughs) What would\Nyou guys do without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Harriet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ooh.\N- Thought you said
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,your Semblance was like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've seen other speed Semblances before,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but that was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's more\Ngoing on than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait until she sees what\Nshe can do with her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lucky catch, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmm, no, I'd chalk\Nthat one up to talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Atlas Control, this is\NClover. Mission accomplished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, thanks for the lift!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N(light buzzes)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Tyrian] Me? Oh, well,\NI'm... someone just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who wants
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to mix things up around here (laughs).
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ah, ah! (screams)
